<main class="traj-page">
  <div class="traj-content-container">
    <h1 class="traj-title">Intersubject — Project Overview</h1>
    <p class="traj-subtitle">A practical web app for mapping shared viewpoints.</p>

    <section>
      <h2 class="traj-heading">Purpose</h2>
      <p class="traj-text">
        Intersubject helps groups see where their ideas overlap and differ.  
        It turns short text statements into clear visual cohorts, offering quick insight for teams, educators, and communities.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="traj-heading">Applications</h2>
      <ul class="traj-list">
        <li class="traj-list-item"><strong>Education:</strong> Measure shared understanding and classroom feedback.</li>
        <li class="traj-list-item"><strong>Organizations:</strong> Align values, priorities, or feedback across teams.</li>
        <li class="traj-list-item"><strong>Coaching:</strong> Track mindset changes over time.</li>
        <li class="traj-list-item"><strong>Research:</strong> Cluster open responses into meaningful trends.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="traj-heading">Technical Outline</h2>
      <ul class="traj-list">
        <li class="traj-list-item"><strong>Stack:</strong> Node.js, Express, EJS, PostgreSQL (Neon Cloud).</li>
        <li class="traj-list-item"><strong>Features:</strong> Auth system, cohort creation, overlap mapping, responsive design.</li>
        <li class="traj-list-item"><strong>Deployment:</strong> Lightweight build suitable for Vercel or standard Node hosting.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="traj-heading">Project Scope</h2>
      <ul class="traj-list">
        <li class="traj-list-item"><strong>Small (1–3 days):</strong> Static pages, layout fixes, or CSS improvements.</li>
        <li class="traj-list-item"><strong>Medium (4–7 days):</strong> Full CRUD apps with auth and database connections.</li>
        <li class="traj-list-item"><strong>Larger (1–2 weeks):</strong> Multi-user dashboards or feature extensions.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="traj-heading">Project Links</h2>
      <ul class="traj-list">
        <li class="traj-list-item"><strong>Live:</strong> <a href="https://intersubject.com">intersubject.com</a></li>
        <li class="traj-list-item"><strong>Portfolio:</strong> <a href="https://williamteach.pro">williamteach.pro</a></li>
        <li class="traj-list-item"><strong>GitHub:</strong> <a href="https://github.com/williamt2045">github.com/williamt2045</a></li>
      </ul>
    </section>

